<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Creamy Butter Linguini with Asparagus & Veggies</h1>
    <p>A bright and comforting dish, loaded with greens and wrapped in a rich, buttery sauce—perfect for family dinners (kid-approved!).</p>
  </header>

  <img src="smallerBanner.jpg" alt="Creamy Butter Linguini with Veggies" class="hero">
 
<body>
  <h2 style="text-align: center;">Ingredients</h2>
  

  <section class="grid">
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> 1 cup
      <p>Fresh Asparagus</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> 1 cup fresh or frozen
      <p>Green Peas</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> 1 small
      <p>Zucchini</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> 1 cup
      <p>Baby Spinach</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> 1 tablespoon
      <p>Lemon</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> 1 cup
      <p>Pecorino Romano</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> 2 tablespoons
      <p>Unsalted Butter</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      
      <p>1 Garlic Clove</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-item">
      <p> Half a pack
      <p>Linguini (serves 3)</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <body>
    <h2 style="text-align: center;">4 Easy Steps</h2>
  <section class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <img src="icon-step1.jpg" alt="Step 1">
      <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> Boil linguini until al dente. In the last 2 minutes, toss in asparagus and peas. Drain and reserve ½ cup pasta water.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <img src="icon-step2.jpg" alt="Step 2">
      <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Sauté garlic and zucchini in butter and olive oil until tender.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <img src="icon-step3.jpg" alt="Step 3">
      <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Add cream, cheese, and lemon zest to the skillet. Simmer and season to taste.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <img src="icon-step4.jpg" alt="Step 4">
      <p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Toss in pasta, veggies, and spinach. Stir gently to coat, adding pasta water as needed.</p>
    </div>
    <img src="veggies.png" alt="veggies">
  </section>

  <div class="blurb">
    Creamy, comforting, and packed with fresh veggies, this dish is a tasty way to sneak greens onto the table. Even picky eaters will love twirling buttery pasta strands—and you’ll love how easy it is to make!
  </div>
